      • onSave

        public void onSave​(javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent)
            throws java.io.IOException
        RUNTIME ERROR. onSave would not switch to the main screen when modifying a part (however it would switch when adding a part) unless a separate ActionEvent (ex: deleting a part, or adding a part) occurred prior. To solve that issue, I created two new functions for updating and adding a new part (updatePart and addNewPart) and threw much of the code from onSave into them.
